HEADWORD: Lammas
<hw>Lam"mas</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>hl⟦amac⟧mmesse</ets>, <ets>hl⟦amac⟧fm⟦ae⟧sse</ets>, loaf mass,
